135	  // ── uploads (chat attachments) ──────────────────────────────────────────
136	  /**
137	   * Upload a local file as a chat attachment (the UI's "load a file" action).
138	   * `POST /api/uploads` takes base64 + mediaType and returns an AttachmentRef
139	   * (`{id, kind, mediaType, filename?, url}`) that a message then references by id.
